Patty Oja https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patty_Oja 0 Patty Oja is a former model and actress best known for her appearance in the film, Eyes of Laura Mars. She also appeared in the film Mr. Mike's Mondo Video, in Redbook and Viva magazines, and on the cover of Mitchell Gray's The Lingerie Book (ISBN 9780312060930).
